graph TD
    User((Creator)) -->|Uploads/Commands| FrontEnd[Next.js Dashboard]
    FrontEnd -->|GraphQL/REST| Gateway[API Gateway]
    Gateway -->|Auth| AuthService[Auth Service]
    Gateway -->|Trigger Job| Orchestrator[Workflow Orchestrator - Temporal]
    
    subgraph "AI Adaptation Pipeline"
    Orchestrator -->|Task 1| Transcribe[Speech-to-Text Worker]
    Orchestrator -->|Task 2| Vision[Scene/Face Detection Worker]
    Orchestrator -->|Task 3| LLM[LLM Context/Captioning Worker]
    end
    
    subgraph "Production & Delivery"
    Orchestrator -->|Task 4| Rendering[FFmpeg/GPU Render Farm]
    Rendering -->|Save Asset| S3[(Object Storage)]
    Orchestrator -->|Task 5| Distro[Social API Distribution]
    end
    
    S3 --> Distro
    Distro -->|Publish| Platforms{Social Platforms}